cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper deals with image reconstruction using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves processing and combining different frequency bands, which is related to information theory (cs.IT). The use of separate DNNs for processing low and high spatial frequencies, as well as the combination of these DNNs, involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves image recovery, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
